OL,3,CCan renewable energy keep up with the
OL,4,Cincreasing power demands of AI?
OL,6,FCan the expansion of renewable energy
OL,7,Fkeep up with the exponentially
OL,8,Fincreasing power demands of AI? ITV
OL,9,FNews' Science Correspondent Martin
OL,10,FStew explains
OL,12,FWords by ITV News Health and Science
OL,13,FProducer Rhiannon Hopley
OL,15,FIt is one of the biggest changes to
OL,16,Fsociety since the industrial
OL,17,Frevolution: around the world, across
OL,18,Fbusinesses and governments, the race
OL,19,Fto develop and benefit from artificial
OL,20,Fintelligence (AI) is on.
