OL,3,CCan renewable energy keep up with the
OL,4,Cincreasing power demands of AI?
OL,6,FBut countries are simultaneously
OL,7,Ftrying to clean up their green
OL,8,Fcredentials.
OL,10,FAlmost everything we do on our phones,
OL,11,Fthe internet or with AI is linked back
OL,12,Fto data centres. They are huge
OL,13,Fbuildings filled with rows and rows of
OL,14,Fsuper computers.
OL,16,FSome of them are so big they use the
OL,17,Fsame amount of power in a year as a
OL,18,Fcity the size of Cambridge ` and
OL,19,Fdemand is growing.
