OL,6,FSo can the expansion of renewable
OL,7,Fenergy keep up with the exponentially
OL,8,Fincreasing power demands of AI?
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FIn 2020 data centres used a little
OL,16,Fover 1% of the UK's overall
OL,17,Felectricity.
