OL,3,CCan renewable energy keep up with the
OL,4,Cincreasing power demands of AI?
OL,6,FBy 2030, forecasts suggest that could
OL,7,Frise up to nearly 7% - the same amount
OL,8,Fof electrical power used by eight
OL,9,Fmillion homes.
OL,11,FThe biggest driver of that increase is
OL,12,FAI. And it is not just energy that is
OL,13,Funder pressure.
OL,15,FData centres also get really hot ` all
OL,16,Fthose super computers kick out a lot
OL,17,Fof hot air and they need to be kept
OL,18,Fconstantly cool, which requires a lot
OL,19,Fof water.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
