OL,3,CCan renewable energy keep up with the
OL,4,Cincreasing power demands of AI?
OL,6,FIn fact, it is estimated that asking
OL,7,FChatGPT to write you a 100 word email
OL,8,Fuses half a litre of water. If you are
OL,9,Fsending multiple emails a day, that
OL,10,Fcan stack up very quickly.
OL,12,FHowever, the power and water usage of
OL,13,Fexpanding data centres is currently
OL,14,Fhard to quantify.
OL,16,FA report by the Royal Academy of
OL,17,FEngineering calls for the government
OL,18,Fto require mandatory reporting from
OL,19,Ftech companies on their power and
OL,20,Fwater usage.
