OL,3,CCan renewable energy keep up with the
OL,4,Cincreasing power demands of AI?
OL,6,FThey say the expansion of resource-
OL,7,Fhungry AI is creating a higher
OL,8,Fenvironmental risk that could lead to
OL,9,Fcompetition for water and energy in
OL,10,Fthe future.
OL,12,FDetailed monitoring is therefore
OL,13,Fnecessary to manage these risks, says
OL,14,FGopal Ramchurn, a professor of
OL,15,Fartificial intelligence at the
OL,16,FUniversity of Southampton and the
OL,17,Fchief executive of Responsible AI UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
