OL,3,CCan renewable energy keep up with the
OL,4,Cincreasing power demands of AI?
OL,6,F"The worst case scenario if we don't
OL,7,Fget this right, if we don't get this
OL,8,Fdata and don't manage the use of
OL,9,Fnatural resources by data centres, is
OL,10,Fthat we will find ourselves making
OL,11,Fdifficult choices when it comes to who
OL,12,Fhas access to power in the UK - data
OL,13,Fcentres of normal people," he says.
OL,15,FThe recent release of DeepSeek, an AI
OL,16,Fsystem developed in China which claims
OL,17,Fto use less energy than traditional
OL,18,Fmodels, has raised hopes that AI could
OL,19,Fbecome more energy efficient.
