OL,3,CCan renewable energy keep up with the
OL,4,Cincreasing power demands of AI?
OL,6,FThere are also developments in
OL,7,Ftechnology such as Small Modular
OL,8,FReactors - nuclear reactors a tenth of
OL,9,Fthe size of the current power plants -
OL,10,Fthat could provide green energy for
OL,11,Fdata centres.
OL,13,FThis week world leaders and tech
OL,14,Fentrepreneurs are meeting in Paris at
OL,15,Fthe AI Summit.
