OL,3,CCan renewable energy keep up with the
OL,4,Cincreasing power demands of AI?
OL,6,FThere are several high-ranking
OL,7,Fpoliticians including US Vice
OL,8,FPresident JD Vance and the Chinese
OL,9,FVice Premier Zhang Guoqing in
OL,10,Fattendance. They will discuss the use
OL,11,Fof the technology and how it will be
OL,12,Fregulated but ultimately everyone
OL,13,Fwants to be the frontrunner in this
OL,14,Fglobal AI race.
OL,16,FIn the UK, Prime Minister Keir Starmer
OL,17,Fhas already announced his AI action
OL,18,Fplan - a collection of 50
OL,19,Frecommendations he believes will make
OL,20,Fthe UK a superpower in the field.
