OL,3,CCan renewable energy keep up with the
OL,4,Cincreasing power demands of AI?
OL,6,FA spokesperson from the Department for
OL,7,FScience, Innovation and Technology
OL,8,Fsaid the government recognises that
OL,9,Fdata centres "face sustainability
OL,10,Fchanges such as energy demands and
OL,11,Fwater use" and added that many newer
OL,12,Fdata centres are "already addressing
OL,13,Fthese issues".
