OL,3,CCan renewable energy keep up with the
OL,4,Cincreasing power demands of AI?
OL,6,F"UK data centre operators have also
OL,7,Fcommitted to implementing energy
OL,8,Fefficient measures under a Climate
OL,9,FChange Agreement, and through the AI
OL,10,FEnergy Council, we'll also build on
OL,11,Fthis by exploring bold, clean energy
OL,12,Fsolutions ` from next-generation
OL,13,Frenewables to small modular reactors `
OL,14,Fto ensure our AI ambitions align with
OL,15,Fthe UK's net zero goals."
OL,17,FThe UK is uniquely well placed in the
OL,18,FAI race, with the highest per capita
OL,19,Fconcentration of experts in the world
OL,20,F` but the question is how to make it
OL,21,Fwork for everyone.
